title: Africa: Groundbreaking HIV-Prevention Initiative Harnesses AI to Bring Medicine to the People
description: [Daily Maverick] The ePrEP programme represents a significant leap forward in addressing critical challenges in PrEP accessibility, continuity and adherence among transgender women and men who have sex with men.

title: Africa: Sports Minister Receives Africa Sustainability Man of the Year 2023 Award
description: [Leadership] The Honourable Minister of Sports Development, Senator John Owan Enoh, has been honored with the distinguished Africa Sustainability Man of the Year 2023 Award.

title: Africa: Wydad Wield Axe After TotalEnergies CAF Champions League Woes
description: [CAF] Moroccan giants Wydad Casablanca have terminated coach Adel Ramzi's contract following a poor start to their TotalEnergies CAF Champions League campaign.
